Components Needed:
Arduino Uno
Ultrasonic Sensor (HC-SR04)
Red LED
Green LED
Buzzer
Resistors (for LEDs)
Jumper wires
Breadboard

Connections:

Ultrasonic Sensor:
VCC → 5V
GND → GND
Trig → Digital Pin 9
Echo → Digital Pin 10

Red LED:
Positive (long leg) → Digital Pin 3 (via resistor)
Negative → GND

Green LED:
Positive (long leg) → Digital Pin 4 (via resistor)
Negative → GND

Buzzer:
Positive → Digital Pin 5
Negative → GND
